# Defined-risk premium selling. Sell the ~25-delta put, buy the wing 5
# strike points lower: max loss is capped at the width minus the credit,
# which is why this is the r/thetagang starter structure. Manage at 50%
# of the credit or 7 days out, whichever comes first.

strategy "Bull Put Spread on SPY"

universe $SPY

when [rsi] < 60
  write [put_spread delta=25 width=5 dte=30]

close at [profit 50%]
  or [dte 7]

risk [contracts 2]
